### Login Admin
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@smarthub.local",
  "password": "password"
}

### Ambil Semua Inventaris
GET http://localhost:8000/api/equipments
Authorization: Bearer ISI_TOKEN_DI_SINI
Accept: application/json

### Buat Jadwal Peminjaman
POST http://localhost:8000/api/schedules
Authorization: Bearer ISI_TOKEN_DI_SINI
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "equipment_id": 1,
  "room_id": 1,
  "start_time": "2026-05-20 09:00:00",
  "end_time": "2026-05-20 12:00:00",
  "purpose": "Produksi konten video komunitas"
}

### Check-in
POST http://localhost:8000/api/check-ins
Authorization: Bearer ISI_TOKEN_DI_SINI
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "borrowing_schedule_id": 1,
  "condition_before": "Kamera dalam kondisi baik dan baterai penuh"
}

### Check-out
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/check-ins/1/checkout
Authorization: Bearer ISI_TOKEN_DI_SINI
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "condition_after": "Kamera kembali dalam kondisi baik",
  "status": "checked_out"
}
